MESSAGE.value: Improve primer pitch logic
Accessibility improvements to both primer and contact selection
Fix pause/resume of same chunk
Pause should not break other streams first playback state
Remove that annoying scroll to beginning
Primer screen should be landscape
Fix crash on contact picker
Fix crash on moving to share screen immediately after OnBoarding
Fix avatar and username gone missing after entering Settings screen
Update translations for French, PT-PT, PT-BR and Spanish
Invite screen should also be landscape on a tablet
Fix multiple invite screens issue
Narrower primer screen on tablet
New changelog
Bump app version
Fix number retrieval for newer devices
Present account for existing accounts when signing in
Update Realm to version 1.0.0 :up:
Update crashlytics
Update GCM and improve its reliability
Testing new way to playback sound (might fix some Samsung low quality issues)
Update several libraries :up:
Fallback to mono recording for devices that fail to record in stereo
Compare current device with non-stereo able devices upon start
Report Stereo recording failures to server
